de.fhe.wayinc.whereareyou.model

Class SavedImage

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fhe.wayinc.whereareyou.model.SavedImage

  • public class SavedImage
extends java.lang.Object
    This class acts as a model for the saved images. It saves all the data connected to an image, such as the path and displayed information.
